{"tid":2112261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★鳳姐憂中招　要求客人全程戴口罩 只會選擇服務熟客","createTime":"2020-07-17T07:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T13:29:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":74,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"c69f5e56ede480356d56369adbdc2cdd8fa7f331","tid":2112261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"疫情再次反彈，令基層生活更見艱難，對於工作期間需要親密身體接觸的性工作者影響尤甚。《香港01》記者巡視荃灣區內的「一樓一」，發現大部分均沒有營業，光顧的人亦寥寥可數。有受訪的「鳳姐」透露，自年初疫情爆發以來已沒有營業，雖然收入大受影響，但「命仔緊要」也沒有辦法。亦有鳳姐指，疫情下只會選擇服務熟客，希望減低感染病菌的風險，「知道佢哋平時無周圍去，無咁驚囉，新客就唔接喇」。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200716/360536863871733760.jpeg/AEcx7WRj9ie1fZJkIsKYPf5EGJBtNalhJxzydCcc8nQ?v=w1920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200716%2F360536863871733760.jpeg%2FAEcx7WRj9ie1fZJkIsKYPf5EGJBtNalhJxzydCcc8nQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=07ec793f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200716/360536863871733760.jpeg/AEcx7WRj9ie1fZJkIsKYPf5EGJBtNalhJxzydCcc8nQ?v=w1920</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/498976/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%87%91%E9%9B%9E2-%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E7%89%88-%E9%B3%B3%E5%A7%90%E6%86%82%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F498976%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%259B%259E2-%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%2589%2588-%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%25A7%2590%25E6%2586%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=024af213\" data-